That's the extent of its grouping capability. There is no support for managing tasks, worker threads, or lifecycle like modern tools.

ğŸ”» 2. No Built-in Thread Pooling or Task Queue
âŒ Limitation:
ThreadGroup doesnâ€™t manage task submission or reuse threads. You must manually create and start threads every time.

âŒ Bad Example:
java
Copy
Edit
