This might return a stale or incorrect value, especially in multi-core systems.

ğŸ”» 6. No Scheduling or Delayed Execution
âŒ Limitation:
ThreadGroup doesnâ€™t support delayed tasks, recurring tasks, or timeouts.

âœ… Modern Alternative:
Use ScheduledExecutorService:

java
Copy
Edit
